  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conur Life is a 2D open world video game, inspired by the first Grand Theft Auto (GTA), and located in a fictional city in the suburbs of Argentina, called San Hugo, based on the town of Florencio Varela.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your stay in San Hugo you will be able to enjoy a city with areas of both high society and the hood, buy clothes and accessories or get a haircut in the center or on the San Hugo pedestrian street.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/7828ba27a5b2ef1bbc09f6d04fa49af7.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/7828ba27a5b2ef1bbc09f6d04fa49af7.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/7828ba27a5b2ef1bbc09f6d04fa49af7.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can tune up your vehicles at the Mecánico Tejada in front of the plaza, buy weapons at the neighborhood tranza, you can wear the shirts of the popular Argentine teams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/463a7c43d865b4ca1f414270ee3ea348.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/463a7c43d865b4ca1f414270ee3ea348.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/463a7c43d865b4ca1f414270ee3ea348.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you prefer something quieter, tour the city in a \"borrowed\" vehicle with Alexis, the main character of this story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/a649967f5f0595284f9a195bfe255b5e.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/a649967f5f0595284f9a195bfe255b5e.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/a649967f5f0595284f9a195bfe255b5e.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, be careful with the San Hugo police and with the gangs that lead the city, have fun and luck... you will need it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/bbb3766f50dd6d12c1f2f1a4e8473637.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/bbb3766f50dd6d12c1f2f1a4e8473637.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/bbb3766f50dd6d12c1f2f1a4e8473637.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHEATS & CODES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By the way, the game comes with cheats...be careful with the zombies mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/9f6b0899f429256f73a1ea69ca0ccedf.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/9f6b0899f429256f73a1ea69ca0ccedf.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/9f6b0899f429256f73a1ea69ca0ccedf.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR FEEDBACK MATTERS:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conur Life has been developed by a small team.  The ongoing development is shaped by your feedback. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conur Life is a 2D open world video game, inspired by the first Grand Theft Auto (GTA), and located in a fictional city in the suburbs of Argentina, called San Hugo, based on the town of Florencio Varela.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your stay in San Hugo you will be able to enjoy a city with areas of both high society and the hood, buy clothes and accessories or get a haircut in the center or on the San Hugo pedestrian street.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/7828ba27a5b2ef1bbc09f6d04fa49af7.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/7828ba27a5b2ef1bbc09f6d04fa49af7.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/7828ba27a5b2ef1bbc09f6d04fa49af7.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can tune up your vehicles at the Mecánico Tejada in front of the plaza, buy weapons at the neighborhood tranza, you can wear the shirts of the popular Argentine teams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/463a7c43d865b4ca1f414270ee3ea348.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/463a7c43d865b4ca1f414270ee3ea348.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/463a7c43d865b4ca1f414270ee3ea348.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you prefer something quieter, tour the city in a \"borrowed\" vehicle with Alexis, the main character of this story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/a649967f5f0595284f9a195bfe255b5e.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/a649967f5f0595284f9a195bfe255b5e.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/a649967f5f0595284f9a195bfe255b5e.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, be careful with the San Hugo police and with the gangs that lead the city, have fun and luck... you will need it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/bbb3766f50dd6d12c1f2f1a4e8473637.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/bbb3766f50dd6d12c1f2f1a4e8473637.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/bbb3766f50dd6d12c1f2f1a4e8473637.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHEATS & CODES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By the way, the game comes with cheats...be careful with the zombies mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/9f6b0899f429256f73a1ea69ca0ccedf.poster.avif?t=1754299809\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/9f6b0899f429256f73a1ea69ca0ccedf.webm?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888330/extras/9f6b0899f429256f73a1ea69ca0ccedf.mp4?t=1754299809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR FEEDBACK MATTERS:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conur Life has been developed by a small team.  The ongoing development is shaped by your feedback. </p>",
